---
import { withBase } from "../../lib/paths";
---

<section class="home-section reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">判断差异</p>
    <h2>普通 AI 与 SongStyle</h2>
    <div class="comparison-preview">
      <article class="default"><h3>普通 AI 默认</h3><p>更多卡片、更多强调、更多视觉效果，直到重点被淹没。</p></article>
      <article class="songstyle"><h3>SongStyle</h3><p>先确定必要信息与关系，再让空间、色彩和动效完成恰当表达。</p></article>
    </div>
    <a class="quiet-link" href={withBase("/examples/comparisons/")}>查看完整对比 <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
  </div>
</section>
